text: Tom Williams (born 30 July 1996) is a Welsh rugby union player who plays for the Ospreys as a wing. Born in Shrewsbury, England, he was a Wales under-20 and Wales Sevens international. Williams made his debut for the Ospreys in 2017 having previously played for the Ospreys academy, RGC 1404, Swansea RFC and the Ospreys Development team. He made his Pro14 debut on 8 September 2018 against the Cheetahs. == References == == External links == *Ospreys Player Profile Category:Sportspeople from Shrewsbury Category:Welsh rugby union players Category:Ospreys (rugby union) players Category:Living people Category:1996 births
